            "translation": "[1872] Say, O disbelievers,",
            "footnotes": [
                {"id": 1872, "note": "Al-Kafirun: The Disbelievers. The Prophet (s.a.v) mentioned that this surah is disassociation from shirk (worship of anything other than Allah) for him who recites it. (Narrated by Aúmad, Abu Dawud and at-Tirmidhi – hasan.)"}
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "لَآ أَعْبُدُ مَا تَعْبُدُونَ",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "page": 603,
            "sajda": false,
            "audio": "https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.saoodshuraym/6209.mp3",
            "translation": "I do not worship what you worship.",
            "footnotes": []
        },
        {
            "text": "وَلَآ أَنتُمْ عَٰبِدُونَ مَآ أَعْبُدُ",
